tourBios.carHigh:
Member of the PGA of Canada...Member of the Great Lakes Tour since 2006. Also played the Moonlight Golf Tour.

2013: Earned non-exempt status with rounds of 75-75-74-70 at the 2012 Fall Qualifying School...Only made cut in four starts was a T57 at the Cape Breton Classic. Opened with a pair of even-par 72s before shooting 76-75 on the weekend.
tourBios.personal: Also goes by the name Justin.

dyn.dynBios: Fan of basketball and baseball, favorite golfer is Tiger Woods
dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T57th in 2013 at the Cape Breton Celtic Classic.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks T94th in Total Eagles on the PGA TOUR Canada.
